Your profile includes personal information including your name, title, company name, phone numbers, address, and e-mail address.

To see your profile, click on your name located in the bottom right of thinkParity.

Your profile information is shared with your contacts. Also, your name, title, and company name are visible to all participants of a package.

<p>You can change profile information by entering new details in the profile dialog and pressing the save button. When you save your changes, the updated profile information is immediately broadcast to all your contacts so that they are up-to-date.

If you change your e-mail address, a verification key will be sent to the new e-mail address and your account will be temporarily placed in an inactive state. To reactivate your account, click the 'activate your account' link and enter the verification key.
